Meghan Strange https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meghan_Strange 0 Meghan Strange is an American actress and voice actress. She is best known for her roles as Ruby from The Land Before Time television series and Robin from Sofia the First. She also voiced the character Harley Quinn on Batman: The Brave and the Bold and has appeared in a number of short films and children's TV shows.
